|------|---------|
| `apps/agent-coordinator/src/app/main.py` | agent-coordinator |
| `apps/edge/src/aitbc_edge/main.py` | edge |
| `apps/exchange/simple_exchange_api.py` | exchange |
| `apps/blockchain-event-bridge/src/blockchain_event_bridge/main.py` | blockchain-event-bridge |
| `apps/whisper/main.py` | whisper |
| `apps/ffmpeg/main.py` | ffmpeg |
| `apps/blockchain-explorer/main.py` | blockchain-explorer |
| `apps/coordinator-api/src/app/services/adaptive_learning_app.py` | adaptive-learning |
| `apps/coordinator-api/src/app/services/multimodal_app.py` | multimodal |
| `apps/coordinator-api/src/app/services/modality_optimization_app.py` | modality-optimization |
| `apps/blockchain-node/src/aitbc_chain/gossip/relay.py` | blockchain-p2p (wrapper fix) |
| `apps/blockchain-node/src/aitbc_chain/sync_cli.py` | blockchain-sync (wrapper fix) |
